John Kitzmiller https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Kitzmiller 0 John Kitzmiller (December 4, 1913 – February 23, 1965) was an American actor who worked in his native land, as well as Italy and the United Kingdom. Kitzmiller achieved his greatest fame as a popular and versatile actor in Europe, making an estimated forty European films. He is known for his role in Dr. No. John_Kitzmiller ( December_4_,_1913 – February_23_,_1965 ) was an_American_actor who worked in his_native_land , as_well_as Italy and the_United_Kingdom .
